<template>
	<el-row>
		<el-col :span="24" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
			<el-row type="flex">
				<el-col :span="12">					
				</el-col>			
				<el-col :span="12">
					<el-input :placeholder="$t('default.TIPS.CLIENT.INPUT_SEARCH')" v-model="search">
						<el-button slot="prepend" icon="el-icon-search"></el-button>
					</el-input>
				</el-col>
			</el-row>
		</el-col>
		<el-col :span="24">
			<el-tabs v-model="activeName">
				<!-- 看诊预约 -->
				<el-tab-pane :label="$t('default.MODULE.APPOINTMENT.APPOINTMENT')" name="first">
					<el-table height="250" :data="data" border>
						<el-table-column prop="date" label="日期" width="180"></el-table-column>
						<el-table-column prop="name" label="姓名" width="180"></el-table-column>
						<el-table-column prop="address" label="地址"></el-table-column>
					</el-table>
				</el-tab-pane>
				<!-- 赴日预约 -->
				<el-tab-pane :label="$t('default.MODULE.APPOINTMENT.APOMT_TO_JA')" name="second">
					<el-table height="250" :data="data" border>
						<el-table-column prop="date" label="日期" width="180"></el-table-column>
						<el-table-column prop="name" label="姓名" width="180"></el-table-column>
						<el-table-column prop="address" label="地址"></el-table-column>
					</el-table>
				</el-tab-pane>
			</el-tabs>
		</el-col>
	</el-row>
</template>

<script>	
	export default {
		data(){
			return {
				search:"",
				data:[],
				activeName:this.$t('default.MODULE.APPOINTMENT.APPOINTMENT'),
			}
		},		
		methods:{
			async getData(){
				
			},			
		}
	}
</script>
